race.comment: PORT RIVER BILLIE (10) has placed four of her past five starts and looks to be in the doorstep of another victory. Graham sticks in the saddle following that last-start placing over this track and trip and rates the testing material against this line-up. BEE EXACT (5) boasts a win over this course and distance and is usually thereabouts. Can measure up against this line-up. ROYAL GLADIATOR (7) saves his best form for this distance range and will be rock-hard fit for this. In the mix. The well-related TOBA (2) (half to G3 winner Keshi Boom) gets 3kg off with the claim and can run a race while fresh. TREASURER (3) best of the rest in an open race to close out the card.
